This directory will contain a cli program for sending data to Ace High
and performing various queries. This program should not be able to
handle anything but communication with the Ace High plotter.

Possible languages for cli program: python, c++? Discuss portability,
project objectives, productivity e.g.

This directory should also contain a gui program capable of viewing,
rotating, moving and scaling drawings before they are plotted. The
program should also be able to calibrate the machine.

Possible languages for gui program: python, c++? Use GTK/Qt/WxWidgets?